bāhyānāmapi mudrāṇāmeteṣāmeva prajñāguṇānāmanukaraṇātprajñātvamanugantavyam | bāhyānāmeva prajñātvapratipādanārthamayaṃ grantha ityapare |

<commentary>utpannarūpāddevatāṃ pratipādya mantraṃ pratipādayannāha—jalpanamityādi |
ālikālyoḥ prajñopāyarūpayoḥ paramamantratvātsarva eva tadrūpatvājjalpo japa ityeṣa niṣprapañco mantraḥ |</commentary>